---
layout: base.njk
title: quickq 使用文章与教程列表
description: quickq 安装、设备配置、连接维护、账号安全与使用场景文章列表。
permalink: /blog/
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">quickq blog</p>
        <h1>quickq 使用文章与教程列表</h1>
      </div>
      <p>下方「核心教程」优先收录；带时间戳的参考文默认不进入搜索引擎索引。</p>
    </div>
    <h2 style="margin-bottom:20px;">核心教程（可索引）</h2>
    <div class="article-list">
      {% for post in collections.indexablePosts %}
        <article class="article-link">
          {% if post.data.heroImage %}
            <a class="preview-link" href="{{ post.url }}">
              <img class="article-thumb" src="{{ post.data.heroImage | assetUrl }}" alt="{{ post.data.heroAlt or post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
            </a>
          {% endif %}
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | readableDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <h2 style="margin:48px 0 20px;">参考文章（默认 noindex）</h2>
    <div class="article-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
        {% if post.data.generated %}
        <article class="article-link">
          {% if post.data.heroImage %}
            <a class="preview-link" href="{{ post.url }}">
              <img class="article-thumb" src="{{ post.data.heroImage | assetUrl }}" alt="{{ post.data.heroAlt or post.data.title }}" loading="lazy">
            </a>
          {% endif %}
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | readableDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        </article>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
